name: Create Qualtrics directory contacts from new Microsoft 365 Excel worksheet rows
description: Make will watch for new rows in a specified Microsoft 365 Excel worksheet at regular intervals and create directory contacts in Qualtrics. The template uses this [example spreadsheet](https://1drv.ms/x/s!AnDK8KmbvjyFkEymVrVMat-yok3D?e=9MvuA2).
